  • Type Parameters:
    V - is the generic type of the value.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Cloneable, javafx.beans.Observable, javafx.beans.property.Property<V>, javafx.beans.property.ReadOnlyProperty<V>, javafx.beans.value.ObservableValue<V>, javafx.beans.value.WritableValue<V>, JsonSupport, AttributeReadName, AttributeReadValue<V>, AttributeWriteValue<V>, PropertyPath<V>, ReadableProperty<V>, WritableProperty<V>

    public abstract class AbstractRegularProperty<V>
extends AbstractValueProperty<V>
    This is the abstract base implementation of a regular WritableProperty. Here regular means that the value type is not special such as a Collection.
    Since:
    8.0.0

        protected void fireValueChangedEvent()
        Description copied from class: AbstractProperty
        Sends notifications to all attached InvalidationListeners and ChangeListeners. This method is called when the value is changed, either manually by calling WritableValue.setValue(Object) or in case of a bound property, if the binding becomes invalid.
